info.description:
GPicSync geocodes your photos and show them in Google Earth or
export to Google Maps.
Applications like Picasa or Flickr also
read and can use these geolocalisation informations.
GPicSync comes with an easy to use graphical interface and a set of handy tools (GPX
Inspector, Renaming tool, KMZ Generator, Geonames and "Geotagged" metadata, etc)
info.keywords: gis, maps, geolocalization, gps, photos, pictures, geotagging, geocoding, kml, kmz, geocode, windows, linux, geonames
info.name: GPicSync
info.summary: Automatically geocode pictures from your camera and a GPS track log.
